              d="M2 2c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V2zm2 0v14h12V2H4zm6 17a1 1 0 1 0 0-2a1 1 0 0 0 0 2z"
